      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i don't really have time to go to a doctor right now and get blood work done. i've seen people in wellness forums say that loading up on high doses for a few weeks is a normal way to fix a deficiency. wouldn't a doctor just tell me the same thing? like, if i only do it for like 4-6 weeks, how much risk is there really?",
